org.apache.openmeetings.db.entity.record

Class RecordingMetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.openmeetings.db.entity.record.RecordingMetaData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IDataProviderEntity

    @Entity
public class RecordingMetaData
extends Object
implements IDataProviderEntity
    contains meta data about each stream, for example if it is a screen sharing or audio/video stream. There is also a RecordingMetaData.Status value streamStatus, as long as this variable is not set to Status.STOPPED, the recording process will not proceed and start to convert all input sources to a single recording file.
    Author:
    sebawagner
